{"tid":1958512,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"送俾有緣無份嘅你。深夜情歌電台【日語】【手譯】","createTime":"2020-04-04T17:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T17:29:28.000Z","uid":317376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a66347b1364a47df2b355271cb7b09920b92ddd0","tid":1958512,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"哈囉～！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大加號～<br />\n我係阿瑤！<br />\n(係，十個女仔七個叫阿瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼我個姓夠少見)<br />\n&ldquo;唔好俾自己後悔&rdquo; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢一句話應該唔陌生<br />\n係感情上我哋都好習慣會全力以赴<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過現實唔係童話，未必每每有最佳結局<br />\n<br />\n唔知你有無經驗同鐘意嘅人好似係一條平行線上永不交錯呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當發現愛上左一直追求自己嘅人嘅時候對方早已移情別戀之類<br />\n又或者係一直強迫自己迎合對方，改變自己到最後依然係分開左&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢最近都有咁嘅煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明難得相愛，但又俾社會上嘅種種事情搞亂曬自己嘅plan. 唔通我哋真係注定係「牛奶同檸檬」？<br />\n<br />\n今日我為咁嘅你帶黎左山本剛嘅《混濁》（cloudy)， 用我N5嘅垃圾水平努力譯左出黎，希望大家鐘意呢首句<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r8acyTaEkRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr8acyTaEkRY&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDD8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=a72a7835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r8acyTaEkRY</a><br />\n<br />\n歌詞，努力嘅瑤提供:<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">紅茶與檸檬 接著仲有牛奶<br />\n<br />\n錯誤咁放埋左一齊<br />\n<br />\n並唔會溝得埋 單單只係浮左係到<br />\n<br />\n咁樣並唔飲得 簡直就好似&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n你同我兩人 逃避住相愛 一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n無論再點搞拌都好 總係只會分開<br />\n<br />\n如此嘅下午茶時光 只會令人悲傷<br />\n<br />\n只有滿佈烏雲嘅天空  出現係午後嘅時間<br />\n<br />\n難以忘懷 苦惱嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n我怨恨住你 亦怨恨住自己<br />\n<br />\n破破碎碎嘅心<br />\n<br />\n(面對）如此沉重嘅每一日 將道別嘅說話<br />\n輕輕細訴<br />\n<br />\n檸檬同埋牛奶 儘管地下沉啦<br />\n<br />\n如此嘅下午茶時光 只會令人悲傷<br />\n<br />\n只會係&ldquo;我好遺憾&rdquo;</div>"},{"pid":"947e9fe48ed8c8c07b413a8d59cd1686c6fcb596","tid":1958512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"thx for sharing. noted with thx"},{"pid":"75a10c978761b3516b368a3962856a502ac2c3ad","tid":1958512,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947e9fe48ed8c8c07b413a8d59cd1686c6fcb596","tid":1958512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"thx for sharing. noted with thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"mother fucker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe7833d26a727151a76b14d2a2d438419b5479","tid":1958512,"uid":154557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日先同佢斬纜 好想喊"},{"pid":"7452e9674d5aa0bbc39a8be3628af246703bb873","tid":1958512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75a10c978761b3516b368a3962856a502ac2c3ad","tid":1958512,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947e9fe48ed8c8c07b413a8d59cd1686c6fcb596","tid":1958512,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:11:45.000Z","msg":"thx for sharing. noted with thx"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:13:38.000Z","msg":"mother fucker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"同佢嚟個farewell night<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n留下美好回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277de02d17d21a282e4d10bf56207deca4ea8833","tid":1958512,"uid":317376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19fe7833d26a727151a76b14d2a2d438419b5479","tid":1958512,"uid":154557,"like":0,"disli